column4: <content>Documents to be reprinted: 1) Entry in Liggeren Rombouts-Lerius I, 1864, p.175; 2) Jonghelinck 1566; 3) Guicciardini 1567, p. 134 (130?); Vasari 1568; - Tombstone (van Bastelaer)-; 5) Lampsonius 1572; 6) Ortelius Epitaph; 7) Morillion Letter to Granvelle; 8) Inventories Archduke Ernst; 9) van Mander 1604: Lehrgedicht+ Life; 10) Imperial Inventories; Arias Montanus to Ortelius 30 March 1590; Coornhert to Ortelius; Granvelle inventory; Letter from Jan Br. to Borromeo 6 March 1609 ([Giovanni] Crivelli [= Giovanni Breughel : pittor fiammingo o sue lettere e quadretti esistenti presso l'Ambrosiana, Milano: Ditta Boniardi-Pogliani di Ermeneg. Besozzi, 1868], p. 118); 1561 Scipio Fabius; 1565 Ortelius; Ortelius correspondence references to B. 1578 15.7 letter from Coornhert to Ortelius.</content>
